data.description: DO NOT PASS THIS DEAL UP!!!!!  Nestled in a Quiet East Cobb Community!  The Unicorn of all Family Homes!  Ranch on a Finished Basement WITH Exterior Access to the Massive Backyard!  Updated throughout the Home you have a Beautiful White Cabinet Kitchen with Quartz Countertops and Full Stainless Steel Appliances Package.  Laminate Flooring throughout the home with Carpet in the Bedrooms and Basement Area.  The Basement Boasts Additional Space that can Support an Office or Gym or even a Workshop!  Prime Location close to Shopping, Parks, Restaurants and Entertainment!  This Home is also in The Kincaid Elementary School Cluster giving you some of East Cobb's Best Schools!  Don't Miss Out on This Great Opportunity!
